      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. It has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and meticulously maintained, with all service records documented. Buyers can expect a car that looks, smells, and drives like new, making it a perfect example for a serious collector or enthusiast.",
