    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's perfect for someone looking for a solid value! This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it, making it a great choice for a daily commuter or a first car. It shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a functional and practical option for anyone ready to give it a little extra care.",
